Year 14 which is also 11, Pauni 9, has paid to the bank in Diospolis that Asklepiades is in charge of, 
for tari(ch ),  Psenamounis, two thousand ⟨dr.⟩, that is, 2,000 ⟨dr.⟩. For kedria, five hundred ⟨dr.⟩, that is,
500 ⟨dr.⟩. Through Asklepiades. 2,900 ⟨dr.⟩. Translation: from edition with slight modifications
